# 🚀 Auto Price Dashboard

Modern dashboard untuk mengelola produk, harga, dan stok. Cocok untuk simulasi automation marketplace seperti Eldorado.gg.

![Preview](Preview.png)

---

## ✨ Features

### 💼 Core Features

* 📦 Add / Delete Product
* 💰 Dynamic Pricing (No Limit Input)
* 📊 Dashboard Summary (Total Product, Stock, Active)
* 🔍 Live Search Filter
* 🔄 Toggle Active / Pause Product

---

### ⚡ UI / UX

* 🎨 Clean Dark Modern UI
* 📱 Fully Responsive (Mobile Friendly)
* ✨ Smooth Animation & Hover Effects
* ⚡ Fast Performance (Vanilla JS)

---

### 🧠 Logic System

* 💾 Local Storage (Auto Save Data)
* ✔️ Input Validation (No Empty Field)
* 🔢 Flexible Number Input (No Limit Price)

---

